       Craken watched the talons slide across his armor, sending a small 
dazzle of sparks to the ground. What was left behinde was several silver 
slashes. Craken responded by pointing both chain guns at prowl and letting 
the deafining bullets explode out.

       The EMP blasts made dents in the CF plate they were behinde. Hell 
Beast glanced up to see that it was coming from the Element. They would have 
to change locations, quickly. No use in fighting a ship.
       "You two, get into your vhicle modes and get us the hell out of here." 
He commanded Rampage and Tankkor. Both bots did as they were told.
       Hell Beast mounted Rampages tank mode, while inferno climed on 
Tankkor. They shot forward, excelerating at an easy 80 mph. The EMP blasts 
exploded all around them, but Hell Beast and the other 3 were most concerned 
out was bombarding the CF shields, now visably failing.

--part1_dc.4db3e43.280b7d95_boundary
